               </para.body>
            </para>
         </proof.block.body>
      </proof.block>
      <proof.block>
         <logic>
            <part.ref>ZeroLessOne</part.ref>
         </logic>
         <caption>ZeroLessOne</caption>
         <proof.block.body>
            <para>
               <para.body>By axiom, <math>
                     <latex>0\neq 1</latex>
                  </math>. So we just learned that</para.body>
            </para>
         </proof.block.body>
      </proof.block>
   </proof>
</theorem>
